{"tid":1295134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北俊︰自由黨應為無攔住政府強推修例負責　促張宇人辭行會成員","createTime":"2019-07-08T02:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T02:46:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68aa501cf640c20ac190b271794f044fc9284a78","tid":1295134,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190708/s00001/19d297f5b4c4ba22da0f9ef79a06c45d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F19d297f5b4c4ba22da0f9ef79a06c45d.jpg&h=349ec251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府修訂《逃犯條例》引發連串示威及遊行活動，自由黨榮譽主席田北俊表示，政府在6月9日反修例大遊行後，仍然堅持如期在6月12日將修例草案直上立法會大會二讀，自由黨當時發聲明支持政府，田北俊認為，當時做法倉卒是失誤，他認為自由黨要為沒有「攔住」政府強推修例負責，因此呼籲身兼行會成員的自由黨飲食界議員張宇人，辭去行會成員一職。<br />\n<br />\n田北俊今早（8日）在商台節目中表示，他與周梁淑儀、方剛、劉健儀4名自由黨榮譽主席，今日將去信張宇人，要求他辭去行會成員一職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190708/s00001/1562552514015/【逃犯條例】田北俊-自由黨應為無攔住政府強推修例負責-促張宇人辭行會成員\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F1562552514015%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E4%BF%8A-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E6%87%89%E7%82%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%94%94%E4%BD%8F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BC%B7%E6%8E%A8%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC-%E4%BF%83%E5%BC%B5%E5%AE%87%E4%BA%BA%E8%BE%AD%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=028d36f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F1562552514015%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E4%BF%8A-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E6%87%89%E7%82%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%94%94%E4%BD%8F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BC%B7%E6%8E%A8%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC-%E4%BF%83%E5%BC%B5%E5%AE%87%E4%BA%BA%E8%BE%AD%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1&h=b3f441f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190708/s00001/1562552514015/【逃犯條例】田北俊-自由黨應為無攔住政府強推修例負責-促張宇人辭行會成員</a>"},{"pid":"8bad55919f7e314788e25ae6b1f48a8ccf1f13b3","tid":1295134,"uid":43116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:42:10.000Z","msg":"不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！"},{"pid":"8d00fdaf758fb760919337c24ca7fbd6514e82e8","tid":1295134,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:44:57.000Z","msg":"依家個行會 入來做咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b8b902ffc6ef2bc0bde3618b8fa2b5ce27bf55","tid":1295134,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d00fdaf758fb760919337c24ca7fbd6514e82e8","tid":1295134,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:44:57.000Z","msg":"依家個行會 入來做咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"好多星期無開會，777被人割蓆割到爛晒"}]}